data.description: Beautiful home situated on 1.2 acres with majestic trees! Iron fence entry with an extended driveway and additional concrete slab added for parking. 4 bedroom or 3 bedroom with an office, separate dining room, and 2 1/2 bathrooms. Exceptional floor plan usage! Split floor plan with no carpet, wood and wood laminate installed in bedrooms, high ceilings, open kitchen with an abundance of cabinet space and expansive countertop space. Spacious primary bedroom with dual vanity bathroom, tub/shower separate, and walk-in multi-closets. 2nd and 3rd bedroom have a Jack & Jill bathroom. Energy savings include solar screens and solar panel system (seller has no electric bill). Oversized covered back patio with a hot tub and spacious backyard provides opportunity for endless options! 2 car carport with a 10x20 shop with lighting fixtures installed. Water filter system installed. LVISD! Must see!!
